1) Make a separate spreadsheet with only the data you want included in the HTML table. Change any headings to what you will want them to be in the final table.

2) cut and paste this data into http://tableizer.journalistopia.com/.  Choose "no CSS" and then tabelize.  

3) copy and paste the resulting html code into ..., between the <body> and </body> tags

4) at the top of the <body> section, at the top of the html you pasted in, change the table class from "tableizer-table" to "sortable"

5) Copy and paste the entire html code (not just what you pasted in from Tableize) into ...
